*Italian: hertz {{m}} ({{p}}: hertz)
*Japanese: [[ヘルツ]] (herutsu)
*Polish: herc {{m}}
*Russian: [[герц]] (gerts) {{m}}
*Spanish: [[hercio]] {{m}}, hertz {{m}} ({{p}}: hertz)
*Swedish: [[hertz#Swedish|hertz]]

